        {
            "title": "月租12萬住凶宅？！中半山雅賓利大廈「雙料自殺」戶呎租62元 睇齊正常單位",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">豪宅市場租務暢旺，凶宅亦同樣以高價租出。<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"中半山雅賓利大廈\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:中半山雅賓利大廈;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4c7ilFE\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">中半山雅賓利大廈</a>一個曾發生「雙料自殺」的凶宅單位，最新以月租12萬元租出，實用呎租約62元，與正常同類單位月租水平相若。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">相關消息：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"劉鑾雄家族1億沽中半山The Albany 創屋苑近5年新高 賬賺1200萬\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:劉鑾雄家族1億沽中半山The Albany 創屋苑近5年新高 賬賺1200萬;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4ktLT3M\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">劉鑾雄家族1億沽中半山The Albany 創屋苑近5年新高 賬賺1200萬</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"前律政司長鄭若驊丈夫潘樂陶沽貨 羅便臣道1號複式戶5,500萬易手 7年巨蝕2,380萬\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:前律政司長鄭若驊丈夫潘樂陶沽貨 羅便臣道1號複式戶5,500萬易手 7年巨蝕2,380萬;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4s6dAC0\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">前律政司長鄭若驊丈夫潘樂陶沽貨 羅便臣道1號複式戶5,500萬易手 7年巨蝕2,380萬</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場消息指出，上述單位為雅賓利大廈一個中層單位，實用面積1,948方呎，屬3房雙套間隔，最新以月租約12萬元租出，實用呎租約62元。翻查資料，2010年該單位租客因生意失敗，在單位內先用利刀割頸，後從大廳攀窗而出跳樓身亡，當時單位租金約10萬元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-416653c0-afc4-3bf5-a7ff-9771dab46755-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據報道，該單位業主為內科專科醫生周一彪，是食物及衞生局前局長周一嶽胞兄，於2005年透過公司名義以3,780萬元購入該單位，以現時月租計，租金回報約3.8厘。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雅賓利大廈由太古發展，位於中半山傳統豪宅地段，於1989年4月開始落成，是一座樓高33層的單棟建築，共提供84戶。根據Squarefoot網站資料，雅賓利大廈現時有10個單位放租，實用面積均由1,308呎至1,948呎，租金由90,000元至16,000萬元，呎租由56.5元至82.1元，意味著上述凶宅單位租金與正常單位相若。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">而且以中半山豪宅為例，同樣水平呎租已可入駐<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"帝景園\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:帝景園;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4bYsVP3\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">帝景園</a>3房套，實用面積1,522呎，叫租9.8萬元，呎租64.4元；</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2hNrJYujUqP4RbAv.9.EZA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/74eb4d3a8d65f8639ee85f0c434a1d89\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">或者<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"竹林苑\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:竹林苑;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4tjEAir\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">竹林苑</a>3房套，實用面積1,442呎，叫租7.9萬元，呎租54.8元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nP5htZfdfqH2D3_VPR3AYg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/58d68f65198dff25892a324830cd248e\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">通常凶宅單位或相鄰單位租盤比市價低20%至40%，視乎事故嚴重程度，同層單位亦有10%至20%的租金折讓。另外，當準租客查問其地產代理單位內是否曾經有不幸事件發生，地產代理須據其所知及所掌握的資料如實作答。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"羅便臣道1號\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:羅便臣道1號;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/羅便臣道1號-798\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">羅便臣道1號</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"雅賓利大廈\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:雅賓利大廈;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/雅賓利大廈-5008\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">雅賓利大廈</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"帝景園\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:帝景園;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/帝景園-787\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">帝景園</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"竹林苑\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:竹林苑;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/竹林苑-812\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">竹林苑</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"中半山\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:中半山;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/中半山-27340\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">中半山</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀:</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"新聞連結\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:新聞連結;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/news/%E6%9C%88%E7%A7%9F12%E8%90%AC%E4%BD%8F%E5%87%B6%E5%AE%85-%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%8A%E5%B1%B1%E9%9B%85%E8%B3%93%E5%88%A9%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88-%E9%9B%99%E6%96%99%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA-%E6%88%B6%E5%91%8E%E7%A7%9F62%E5%85%83-%E7%9D%87%E9%BD%8A%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D-75399\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新聞連結</a>。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"28Hse App\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:28Hse App;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/appdownload\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">28Hse App</a>。</p></div>",
