        {
            "title": "短炒波士｜港股續受戰事影響 留意中長線分水嶺｜Ringo",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KsRr1O6.hxpqwGBW7_xFUA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/1a065fef5d6bd3fe390848e3f65559ff\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">港股3月累挫近7%，是2024年1月以來表現最差的一個月。股市短期表現仍由美伊局勢主導，短線分水嶺未必有太大效用，反而應留意25,000點的中長線分水嶺。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美伊局勢難料，投資者無須急於入市，可等待局勢進一步明朗且恒指企穩25,000點的中長線分水嶺始出手增持也未算太遲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">個股方面，騰訊（700）早前跌穿500元，預期480元會有較大支持，但寧待其重新企穩500元才追入更為安全。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">泡泡瑪特（9992）績後股價持續插水，由於該股的增長前景未及市場預期，相信市場會對其估值重新定價，該股料仍有下行空間，故不宜撈底，但此水平追沽的風險則較大，因技術性反彈會隨時出現。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6de7fbc2-385c-3f98-8f51-8dca52efd70c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市況動盪之下，包括內銀股防守性股份較受追棒。然而，內銀股升幅較慢，若美伊局勢好轉，表現料將跑輸成長股，故投資者應先保留現金，等待市況好轉追入估值近期已跌至吸引水平的成長股，其回報料優於現時才買入防守性股份。若要選擇銀行股，本地銀行股或美國銀行股更為值搏。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美股方面，台積電（TSM）自近期高位回調兩成，但主因市場氣氛影響，與其業務無關，現價已可小注吸納。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">金價近期出現回調，但下行空間料已不大，4,300美元將有較大支持，若向上突破4,600美元，可再睇高一線至4,800美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Ringo<br/>資深投資者<br/>註：專欄作家言論不代表本網立場</strong></p><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://signup.hkiei.com/ringo_webinar_bossmind\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"686\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ImrasCUjN02l5wpgg5PUdQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/f52012128630469615370091d56ff897\" width=\"960\"/></div></a></div>",
